{"word":"H2674 - חָצֹור - Châtsôwr - khaw-tsore' - Hazor","slug":"H2674","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָצֹור</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Châtsôwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-tsore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hazor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>חצור</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>châtsôr</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>khaw-tsore'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Hazor = \"castle\" <ol><li>a royal city of northern Palestine allotted to Naphtali</li><li>one of the cities of Judah in the extreme south</li><li>a town north of Jerusalem in which the Benjamites resided after the return from exile</li><li>a site in Arabia</li></ol> <p />Origin: a collective form of <a href=\"#/H2691\">H2691</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2675\">H2675</a>, <a href=\"#/H2681\">H2681</a>, <a href=\"#/H2691\">H2691</a>, <a href=\"#/H2692\">H2692</a>, <a href=\"#/H2693\">H2693</a>, <a href=\"#/H2694\">H2694</a>, <a href=\"#/H2695\">H2695</a>, <a href=\"#/H2696\">H2696</a>, <a href=\"#/H2697\">H2697</a>, <a href=\"#/H2698\">H2698</a>, <a href=\"#/H2699\">H2699</a>, <a href=\"#/H2700\">H2700</a>, <a href=\"#/H2701\">H2701</a>, <a href=\"#/H2702\">H2702</a>, <a href=\"#/H2703\">H2703</a>, <a href=\"#/H2704\">H2704</a>, <a href=\"#/H2705\">H2705</a>"}]}